<item>
            <title>[SOLR-2492] DIH does not commit if only Deletes are processed</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-2492</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If a DIH run processes deletes using the $deleteDocById and/or $deleteDocByQuery special commands, and if no adds or updates get processed in the same run, then &quot;commit&quot; is never called.  Also, the # of deleted documents does not get incremented.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12506100">SOLR-2492</key>
            <summary>DIH does not commit if only Deletes are processed</summary>
